      = button_link 'Try a question now', '/gym/exercises/any', color: 'primary', size: 'lg'
      %p{ style: 'margin-top: 10px;' }
        Or try a specific kind of question:
        = succeed ',' do
          = link_to 'multiple choice', random_exercise_path(question_type: 1)
        = succeed ',' do
          = link_to 'Java', random_exercise_path(language: 'Java')
